      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔表示货币政策调整时机已经到来，引发全球市场风险偏好回升，新兴市场资产随之上涨。]]></description>
